<L>__{exterior country store day}
<A>__{thelma has tears running down her face and she is watching the ground as she storms back to the car. so she makes a loud grunt as she slams into someone that she did not see. both people are knocked back a few steps from the force of the collision.}
<C>__{hitchhiker}
<D>__{whoa! excuse me! miss, are you alright?}
<A>__{thelma nods her head "yes," but tears continue. her crying is silent.}
<C>__{hitchhiker}
<D>__{is there anything i can do?}
