<C>__{thelma}
<D>__{no. thanks. sorry.}
<B>__{thelma}
<A>__{collects herself as she walks back to the car. she gets in and is drying her eyes, looking in the side mirror. in the mirror she sees the hitchhiker come back around from the side of the building. he is several feet behind the car, and she watches him as he removes his long sleeved shirt and stuffs it into his duffel bag. now he is just in t shirt and jeans. he looks good. really good. she watches in the mirror as he picks up his stuff and heads towards the road. she can see him as he's walking. he stops. he's thinking. he heads over to the car.}
<C>__{hitchhiker}
